data.description: Classic Clintonville home lovingly remodeled by owner of 12 years. Completely new kitchen and bathroom with refinished hardwood floors, fully fenced yard, large 2 car garage and off street parking in alley, new landscaping, sidewalk, and rear patio! New roof and gutters 2020, New furnace 2018, new AC 2023. Quartz countertops, all new windows, fresh paint, this home has been brought back to life for you to enjoy! The kitchen and dining room have been opened up for a contemporary feel while maintaining the historic charm of this 91 year old house. Please see agent remarks regarding Columbia Gas plans across the street.
